        <item>
            <title>传微博实施前台实名制　粉丝多于 50 万需公开真名字＋性别</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/16/weibo/fun-tech/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=weibo</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2023/10/16/weibo/fun-tech/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Christy]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Mon, 16 Oct 2023 07:50:31 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[科技趣闻]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[实名制]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[微博]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[自媒体]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1199527</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>近日有消息指，微博计划向粉丝人数多于 50 万的自媒体实施前台实名制。若然消息属实，微博将成为首个实施前台实名制的社交平台。</p><p>中国知名财经博主、上海浦东工商联副主席洪榕上周五（13 日）在微博发文，指全网自媒体要实施前台实名制，粉丝人数多于 50 万的用户真名要在一级页前端展示。粉丝可以知道自己关注的自媒体究竟是男是女，是现实中的谁了。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-07.19.05.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1199536" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-07.19.05-694x241.png" alt="" width="694" height="241" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-07.19.05-694x241.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-07.19.05-768x267.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-07.19.05.png 1260w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>洪榕随后补充，多于 100 万名粉丝的自媒体帐号需于 10 月底前于前台展示真实姓名，多于 50 万名的需于 12 月底前展示，而多于 10 万名的则只需在后台完成身份实名认证并于前台展示职业资料。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-07.57.10.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1199539" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-07.57.10-694x217.png" alt="" width="694" height="217" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-07.57.10-694x217.png 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-07.57.10-1280x401.png 1280w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-07.57.10-768x241.png 768w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-07.57.10.png 1436w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></a></p><p>消息一出，各大知名博主纷纷表示洪榕的消息属实。科技博主拆台 CT 转发洪榕的微博并称，微博曾向他征求意见，目前限定的范围是娱乐 、社会和财经，更指除微博外亦有其他大型社交平台向他征求类似意见。</p><p><a href="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-07.57.39.png"><img decoding="async" loading="lazy" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1199540" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-07.57.39-404x580.png" alt="" width="404" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-07.57.39-404x580.png 404w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-07.57.39-626x900.png 626w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2023/10/萤幕截图-2023-10-16-07.57.39.png 710w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 404px" /></a></p><p>图片来源：电玩帮、微博</p><p>资料来源：<a href="https://www.vgover.com/news/61952">电玩帮</a></p><h2> 最新影片</h2><div class="video-container"><iframe loading="lazy" title="最新影片" width="500" height="281" src="https://www.youtube.com/embed/videoseries?list=PLiEPZioiGtHw9_9gm4Ty0_pTEviOKNvfl" frameborder="0" allow="accelerometer; autoplay; clipboard-write; encrypted-media; gyroscope; picture-in-picture; web-share" allowfullscreen=""></iframe></div></p>
]]>
            </description>
